title: Buy Osell Beckham? l The Dantasy Football Podcast
description:
Danny Kelly, Danny Heifetz, and Craig Horlbeck debate who they’d trade for Odell Beckham Jr., explore who to add after injuries to Marlon Mack and Davante Adams, and discuss how Craig’s middle school nemesis is the no. 2 fantasy tight end through Week 4.
